{"tid":2151370,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE子瑜新髮色曝光 仙氣十足超顯白","createTime":"2020-08-11T10:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T13:00:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"80179713d895902aab68d3425ca0ec6e22c7b62a","tid":2151370,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:55:49.000Z","msg":"由於受到新冠肺炎的影響，南韓團體最近紛紛舉辦網上演唱會、視像簽售等活動，避免偶像跟粉絲的直接接觸。女團TWICE早前也舉辦了出道首個網上演唱會《Beyond LIVE - TWICE : World in A Day》，得到不少粉絲的支持！<br />\n<br />\n成員更特意為演唱會換上新造型，令粉絲相當驚喜！子瑜也把之前的深色髮色漂染成淺橘色，結束演唱會後在官方IG上傳數張照片，吸引了粉絲的注意。<br />\n<br />\n子瑜在IG上分別以中、韓文寫道：「ONCE謝謝你們！今天也從你們身上得到了許多能量！」，感謝粉絲的支持。上傳的照片中，可見子瑜染了一頭淺橘色，並綁了雙馬尾的造型，非常可愛！子瑜更跟成員Momo、多賢一起擺出不同動作拍照，大派福利給粉絲！<br />\n<br />\n粉絲看到照片後紛紛表示：「淺橘色太適合子瑜了！」、「雙馬尾的子瑜太可愛了」、「很期待子瑜之後的表現」等。"},{"pid":"4dbd2cbe16deca574f8d9496222faa820b982e56","tid":2151370,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/08/20200811_twice-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F08%2F20200811_twice-2.jpg&h=013d04fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/08/20200811_twice-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F08%2F20200811_twice-3.jpg&h=cd970463&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c244f257ca5ca5567fed93575f67bc5a168b7e1","tid":2151370,"uid":224453,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4dbd2cbe16deca574f8d9496222faa820b982e56","tid":2151370,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/08/20200811_twice-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmed